President-elect Trump has
spent another day huddling with
advisers on

01:06.033 --> 01:07.701 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
key Cabinet jobs.

01:07.734 --> 01:11.405 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Vice president-elect Mike Pence
led the arrivals
today at Trump Tower in New
York.

01:11.438 --> 01:14.708 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Another adviser dismissed
concerns that Mr.
Trump is staying out of sight.

01:14.741 --> 01:19.379 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN: I think he's -- you know,
he's making
phone calls to leaders and
they're calling

01:19.413 --> 01:20.380 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
him.

01:20.414 --> 01:22.082 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
