place to be
here and watch who's coming and
going.

01:26.186 --> 01:27.955 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And he's just talking as it's
appropriate.

01:27.988 --> 01:32.492 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The
president-elect was
heard from today on losing the
popular vote

01:32.526 --> 01:34.261 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to Hillary Clinton.

01:34.294 --> 01:37.798 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
