08:11.791 --> 08:15.595 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
How is that influencing some of
the decisions
that he has in front of him now?

08:15.628 --> 08:17.364 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ALEX ISENSTADT: It's unclear.

08:17.397 --> 08:22.469 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it's also unclear exactly
how this is
shaping who is going to be
getting some of

08:22.502 --> 08:24.237 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
these top posts.

08:24.270 --> 08:27.173 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There was some reporting over
the last day
or so that Trump wanted
clearance for his

08:27.207 --> 08:32.445 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
children and for his son-in-law,
Jared Kushner,
to also be getting these
security clearances.

08:32.479 --> 08:36.616 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
The campaign -- or the
transition committee,
rather, pushed back a little bit
on that reporting.

08:36.649 --> 08:40.120 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But, look, it's clear that this
is a guy who
is new to government.

08:40.153 --> 08:44.858 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He's new to this kind of thing,
and he's now
for the first time getting this
information.

08:44.891 --> 08:47.927 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Are transition
teams the
place where you start to reward
your friends

08:47.961 --> 08:52.298 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
