so long and
eventually maybe in government
positions as

08:52.332 --> 08:54.167 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
well?

08:54.200 --> 08:56.936 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ALEX ISENSTADT: Well, look, you
look back
at George W. Bush's
administration, he selected

08:56.970 --> 09:03.376 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
