his family,
to his father, and so you do see
some of that

09:03.410 --> 09:05.145 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
But it's interesting.

09:05.178 --> 09:09.182 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You look at the people who
Donald Trump is
looking at, even people who he
has already

09:09.215 --> 09:11.117 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
selected, Reince Priebus,
Stephen Bannon.

09:11.151 --> 09:15.355 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Those are people who really
played key roles
in his campaign and now are
going to be overseeing

09:15.388 --> 09:16.856 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
his White House.

09:16.890 --> 09:17.757 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: All right,
Alex Isenstadt
of Politico, thanks so much.

09:17.791 --> 09:19.426 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ALEX ISENSTADT: Thank you.

09:19.459 --> 09:23.062 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Just this past
weekend,
president-elect Trump announced
his picks

09:23.096 --> 09:25.365 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
for two key posts in the White
House.

09:25.398 --> 09:28.701 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
RNC Chairman Reince Priebus will
