News.

13:05.284 --> 13:09.889 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: And, Mark, you spent
a lot of time
with Reince Priebus earlier this
year for

13:09.922 --> 13:13.726 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
