qualifications.

15:43.543 --> 15:49.882 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN YANG: And, Josh, you know
both Reince
Priebus and Steve Bannon.

15:49.916 --> 15:54.587 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
