42:08.693 --> 42:14.899 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It was -- it was, she didn't see
herself as
part of that movement, for some
reason.

42:14.932 --> 42:20.471 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILDRED LOVING, Wife of Richard
