able to provide and protect,

44:59.297 --> 45:04.101 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I can take care of you.

45:04.135 --> 45:10.641 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
RUTH NEGGA: I know that.

45:10.675 --> 45:21.185 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOEL EDGERTON: I can take care
of you.

45:21.218 --> 45:26.424 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
RUTH NEGGA: I know.

45:26.457 --> 45:33.197 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOEL EDGERTON: There's an engine
