the passing of a beautiful woman
who contributed

49:19.990 --> 49:22.059 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
so much to my understanding of
the world.

49:22.092 --> 49:25.296 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Our deepest sympathies to all
who knew her.

49:25.329 --> 49:27.264 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
She will be greatly missed.

49:27.298 --> 49:35.172 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
She will forever be a role model
for not just
journalists, but for all young
women.

49:35.206 --> 49:46.150 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: I tell this to young
people all
the time.

49:46.183 --> 49:49.553 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Rather than going around saying,
aha, they
didn't give this to me because I
was black

49:49.587 --> 49:53.357 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
or I was a woman, you stop and
think, they
didn't give it to me because
they couldn't

49:53.390 --> 49:55.192 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
imagine me in this role.

49:55.226 --> 49:59.063 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it's my job then -- it's a
tougher job
than my white counterparts have,
but it's

49:59.096 --> 50:00.297 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
just what it is.

50:00.331 --> 50:04.168 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
My job is to force them to see
me in a different
role.

50:04.201 --> 50:14.245 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And then you act on that.

50:14.245 --> 50:28.759 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And then you act on that.

50:28.792 --> 50:35.733 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's important to be reminded
how easily we
can be denied simple, obvious
opportunities,

50:35.766 --> 50:41.138 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
how low the ceilings can get and
how much
fortitude it takes to refuse to
accept the

50:41.171 --> 50:44.174 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
limits that others place on you.

50:44.208 --> 50:47.344 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But you now have the skills to
transcend those
limits.

50:47.378 --> 50:49.213 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Whose stories can you tell?

50:49.246 --> 50:51.682 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Whose voices are not being
heard?

50:51.715 --> 50:56.020 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Who gets to decide which stories
and voices
get ignored?

50:56.053 --> 50:59.123 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And what are you willing to do
about it?

50:59.156 --> 51:03.894 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MAN: This is Michael from
Texarkana, Texas.

51:03.928 --> 51:06.931 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I'm so saddened to hear of the
loss of Ms.
Ifill.

51:06.964 --> 51:11.936 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
She has counseled me and
explained current
events to me for about 15 years.

51:11.969 --> 51:17.574 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I haven't been able to face much
of the news
and the analysis this past week,
but I thought,

51:17.608 --> 51:23.347 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
when I was ready to get back in
it, she would
help me make sense of it all.

51:23.380 --> 51:25.215 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

51:25.249 --> 51:36.427 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARRY REID (D-NV), Minority
Leader: It really
was too bad that she died at age
61, a woman

51:36.460 --> 51:39.263 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
who was really someone who broke
barriers.

51:39.296 --> 51:45.502 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Every step of her life was
something new and
something inspirational for
those around her.

51:45.536 --> 51:51.008 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I watch as often as I can the
"NewsHour,"
and I will miss her.

51:51.041 --> 51:56.180 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: We live in a world
of extremes,
often petty argument, where we
hide behind

51:56.213 --> 52:02.486 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
our devices to insult one
another in a way
we would never do face to face.

52:02.519 --> 52:06.357 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Technology is fabulous, but this
is not what
it is for.

52:06.390 --> 52:12.596 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have to harness our thinking
and our expressions
to add to the debates around us,
not to debase

52:12.629 --> 52:13.597 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
them.

52:13.630 --> 52:16.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MAN: This is Perry (ph) from
California.

52:16.066 --> 52:20.871 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Her family and colleagues have
lost such a
talented and principled woman.

52:20.904 --> 52:28.178 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
How sad that we lost her during
a time of
such upheaval, when her skills
are needed

52:28.212 --> 52:30.147 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
more than ever.

52:30.180 --> 52:39.089 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Cynics thinks that
they know all
the answers already, and then
they stop listening.

52:39.123 --> 52:44.028 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Skeptics always have more
questions to ask,
but we are willing to be
persuaded to the

52:44.061 --> 52:49.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
honesty of an alternate point of
view, even
if we don't share it.

52:49.266 --> 52:56.673 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Is it possible to be skeptical
and optimistic
and ambitious, open, excited to
possibility

52:56.707 --> 52:59.443 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and willing to change the world
as well?

52:59.476 --> 53:05.249 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
I think so.

